title: Pizza 3 The Mummy
subTitle: Nalan, a restauranteur with a complicated love life, unwillingly gets embroiled in a series of strange events after a miniature mummy sarcophagus ends up in his restaurant.

title: Friday The 13th
subTitle: The 13th page of a mysterious book harbours evil. It gives rise to a series of devastating events as people who read it, get possessed by demonic spirits.

title: Athiratha
subTitle: Following a family legacy, a youngster ventures into journalism and investigates a scandal involving a powerful politician. However, his life moves downhill after he is arrested under a false charge.

title: Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: LIE
subTitle: Sathyam and Chaitra meet unexpectedly in their pursuit of making quick money. Soon, after they fall in love, Sathyam encounters Padmanabham, a criminal on the run from the Indian police.

title: Agent Chanakya
subTitle: Arjun, a highly sought-after RAW agent, is known for his skills at catching some of the most hardened criminals. However, he falls in danger when he goes after Ibrahim Qureshi, a terrorist.

title: Pichaikkaran
subTitle: A rich businessman and a poor beggar's lives intersect, showing how money influences their fates as one fights off greedy predators and the other searches for his long-lost sister.

title: Jaguar
subTitle: Krishna, an orphan medical student, lives a seemingly ordinary life. However, unbeknownst to people, he is a vigilante named Jaguar who pursues a certain group of people in order to kill them.

title: The Warriorr
subTitle: Satya, a doctor, is brutally beaten and driven out of his city by Guru, a ruthless gangster. However, Satya returns two years later as a police officer to exact revenge on Guru.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Dum Man Of Power
subTitle: Tarak comes to India after his parents die in an accident and falls in love with Meera, who seeks others' happiness before hers. Soon, Tarak and Meera's relationship goes through a rough patch.

title: Vijayadasami
subTitle: Disowned by his family, a young man relocates to the city and falls in love with the daughter of a rich businessman. Eventually, he decides to return to his village and challenge his evil brothers.

title: Stalin
subTitle: Stalin, a former army officer, is deeply moved by the suicide of a girl with physical disabilities. So, he devises a plan to extend unconditional help to those who need it to establish peace.

title: The Masterpiece
subTitle: A young man falls in with the wrong crowd and strays from heroic deeds. However, an accidental encounter with danger forces him to change his ways.

title: Harom Hara (The Revolt)
subTitle: Subrahmanyam loses his job and faces financial ruin. In an attempt to overcome his limitations, he gets involved in the illegal arms trade, eventually becoming one of South India's notorious arms dealers.

title: Golmaal 3
subTitle: Cupid strikes when Pritam, a single father, comes across his college sweetheart, Geeta, in Goa. However, when their respective children go at war with each other, the two find it difficult to reunite.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: Inspector Vijay
subTitle: Vijay, an honest police officer, meets Samyukta at a cafe and falls in love with her. However, his life changes when he witnesses a kidnapping and ends up helping a lonely woman, Lavanya.

title: Rider
subTitle: As love blossoms between orphans Chinnu and Kitty, fate separates them as children. However, they grow up yearning to find each other.

title: Ek Aur Vinashak
subTitle: An honest man is forced to turn into a gangster as he strives to make enough money for the treatment of a girl who is comatose.

title: Ek Aur Vinashak
subTitle: An honest man is forced to turn into a gangster as he strives to make enough money for the treatment of a girl who is comatose.

title: Vardi Ki Aan
subTitle: An upright police officer vows to punish the culprits involved in the brutal rape of a young woman. However, his investigations unravel a shocking secret about his own father's despicable crimes.

title: Rowdy Lover
subTitle: An unlikely romance blooms between a soft-hearted thug and his IT consultant neighbor, blending tough exteriors with tender hearts.

title: Don
subTitle: Chakaravarthi, a wayward college student searching for purpose, navigates campus life while grappling with a controlling father and a strict professor.

title: Raththam
subTitle: While investigating his friend's murder, Ranjith, a journalist, unearths the sinister network responsible for a series of crimes.

title: Dil Hai Tumhaara
subTitle: Sarita raises Shalu, her spouse's love child, and her daughter, Nimmi, but she does not forgive Shalu's past. When she discovers that Shalu is growing close to Nimmi's lover, things become worse.

title: Gatta Kusthi
subTitle: Veera has a preconceived set of criteria for what he wants in a bride. However, he ends up unexpectedly marrying a woman who is the complete opposite of his expectations.

title: Captain
subTitle: A captain leads his team of soldiers inside a forest to investigate mysterious disappearances. However, they soon realise that the danger is more than they bargain for.

title: ACP Shiva
subTitle: An IPS officer treads the path of corruption, but when his dishonest ways prove costly, he must decide whether to seek righteous revenge.

title: Tantra
subTitle: Rekha, a woman with the ability to perceive spirits, sees her life take a dark turn when she encounters a sinister black magic practitioner.

title: Ek Aur Rakshak
subTitle: Sandeep, a young man, is prepared to marry Deepthi. However, when she gets kidnapped on their wedding day by a vengeful local thug, Diwakar, Sandeep decides to save her.
